      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit features a precise six-speed manual transmission and a functional M-variable differential lock. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a complete VANOS system refresh and preventative rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true with updated bushings, providing the tactile feedback these chassis are known for. While displaying minor aesthetic patina typical of a well-loved driver, its performance envelope remains sharp and predictable.",
