      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and documented rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its original geometry but benefits from refreshed bushings for sharpened turn-in. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent valve clearances and rod bearing inspection\u2014are optimal for the next enthusiast owner.",
